name: core::<iter::adapters::intersperse::Intersperse<I> as iter::traits::iterator::Iterator>::fold
src:
fn fold<B, F>(self, init: B, f: F) -> B
    where
        Self: Sized,
        F: FnMut(B, Self::Item) -> B,
    {
        let separator = self.separator;
        intersperse_fold(
            self.iter,
            init,
            f,
            move || separator.clone(),
            self.started,
            self.next_item,
        )
    }
